# 8. REFINEMENT DATA

_refine_special_details
; The structure was refined based on the following considerations.
 The perovskite lattice {PbnI3n+1} was refined anisotropically without
 any constraints on the Pb and I atoms. All organic atoms were refined isotropically.
 For the organinc part, the N atoms and C atoms connected directly to N can be easily found. 
 The rest of carbons were found by the Q peaks and restraints were applied to the C-C and C-N bond lengths and bond angles. 
 Each atom was treated as having equivalent thermal parameters. 
;

